<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>E-Learning Activation Mail</title>
    <style>
        .email-wrapper {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            color: #333;
        }
        .email-header {
            background-color: #0070f3;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 18px 24px;
            font-size: 19px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .activation-code {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-align: center;
            letter-spacing: 10px;
        }
        .email-body {
            padding: 24px;
            font-size: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
        }
        .email-body p{
            margin: 0;
            padding: 2px;
        }
        .email-footer {
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #efeded;
            margin-top: 10px;
            padding: 3px 10px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-wrapper">
        <div class="email-header">
            <h1 class="email-heading">Welcome to E-Learning Platform</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="email-body">
            <p>Hello <b><%= user.name %><b>,</p>
            <p>Thank you for registering with us. To activate your account, please use the following activation code.</p>
            <h1 class="activation-code"><%= activationCode %></h1>
            <p>Please enter the code on the activation page. This code will expire in <b>5 minutes.</b></p>
            <p>If you did not register with us, please ignore this email.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="email-footer">
            <p>If you have any questions, please contact us at <a href="mailto:support@e-learning.com">support@e-learning.com</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>